videos.headline: Darboh opens scoring with 34-yard Michigan TD
videos.description: Michigan strikes first as Wilton Speight finds Amara Darboh in the end zone for a 34-yard touchdown to give the Wolverines a 7-0 lead over Maryland.

videos.headline: Peppers, Michigan use trickeration to get big gain
videos.description: Jabrill Peppers takes the handoff, throws it back to quarterback Wilton Speight who fires it downfield to Jehu Chesson for the 40-yard gain to get the Wolverines in the red zone.

videos.headline: Speight runs right up the middle for a Michigan TD
videos.description: Michigan quarterback has a wide-open hole up the middle and takes off for the 10-yard touchdown to double the Wolverines' lead to 14-0 over Maryland.

videos.headline: Smith dives in for 3-yard Michigan TD
videos.description: De'Veon Smith plunges in for a three-yard touchdown to give Michigan a 21-0 lead over Maryland.

videos.headline: Hill muscles in for another Michigan TD
videos.description: The rout is on as Michigan's fullback Khalid Hill plunges in for a one-yard touchdown to give the Wolverines a 28-0 lead over Maryland.

videos.headline: Chesson scores Michigan's fifth TD of the half
videos.description: Wilton Speight finds Jehu Chesson for a 33-yard touchdown to give Michigan a 35-0 lead over Maryland.

videos.headline: Don't try and peek at Harbaugh's play sheet
videos.description: A Michigan coach blocks Jim Harbaugh's play sheet from the aerial camera.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Don't try and peek at Harbaugh's play sheet) 2016/11/05

videos.headline: Smith scores his second of the game for Michigan
videos.description: De'Veon Smith runs in from one yard out to increase Michigan's lead to 45-0 over Maryland.

videos.headline: Smith scores third TD as the blowout continues
videos.description: De'Veon Smith runs in the touchdown from two yards out as Michigan increases its lead to 52-3 over Maryland.

videos.headline: Delano Hill grabs second INT on the day
videos.description: Caleb Rowe pass intercepted Delano Hill return for no gain to the Mich 17

videos.headline: J. O'Korn pass,to K. Crawford for 9-yards for a TD
videos.description: John O'Korn pass complete to Kekoa Crawford for 9-yards for a TD

videos.headline: Michigan cruises past Maryland
videos.description: No. 3 Michigan gets 362 passing yards and three total touchdowns from quarterback Wilton Speight in a 59-3 win over Maryland.

videos.headline: Peppers all over the field yet again
videos.description: Jabrill Peppers didn't score a touchdown in Michigan's 59-3 rout of Maryland, but he still brought his trademark excitement on offense and defense.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Peppers all over the field yet again) 2016/11/5 ESHEET ENHL
